Skilton, Respondent, v. Automatic Bank Punch Co., Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. November 18, 1890.) Appeal from first district court.

Argued before Daly, C. J., and Bischoff and Pryor, JJ.

Beltz & Large, for appellant. J. M. Ferguson, for respondent.

Ho opinion. Judgment affirmed, with costs.
